      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i get that and i appreciate the caution but can you just tell me straight—is there any medical reason why 2mg would be dangerous if my blood results have been fine? like, if i've been consistent and feeling 100%, wouldn't a lower dose just be more efficient and less taxing on my system? i just need some reassurance to know if i'm crazy for thinking i can taper down myself.",
